# 🧙 Hogwarts House Selector

A fun quiz website that sorts you into a Hogwarts house (Gryffindor, Hufflepuff, Ravenclaw, or Slytherin).  
Built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

## 🔗 Demo
[Live Demo](https://your-username.github.io/hogwarts-house-selector/)  

## ✨ Features
- Interactive quiz with multiple-choice questions  
- Shows your Hogwarts house result at the end  
- Pure frontend (no backend required)  

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Download or clone this repo  
2. Open `index.html` in your browser  

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript  

